#### Q55. Which URL pattern should you follow for accessing a subresource attached to a specific resource?

- %OPTION% /companies/employees/{companyId}/{employeeId}
- %OPTION% /company/{companyId}/employees/{employeeId}
- %OPTION% /companies/{companyId}/employees/{employeeId}
- %OPTION% /companies/{companyId}/employee/{employeeId}

[Resource Naming](https://restfulapi.net/resource-naming/)
